@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ahosni(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.exp(0.14))
    tmp = 0.82
    v0 = 0.16
    tmp = v0
    v2 = ((wp.abs(tmp + 0.17) + wp.cos(v0 + 0.77)) * ((v2 + 0.07 * tmp + 0.79) + (v1 + 0.08 * v1 + 0.59)))
    v2 = (wp.sin(wp.exp(v0 + 0.58)) / (v2 * wp.exp(v1 + 0.31)))
    data[tid] = v0
